Define Documentation

#define equalTo   HC_equalTo

equalTo(object) - Is the object equal to another object, as tested by the -isEqual: method?

If the given object is nil, the matcher will match nil.

Synonym for HC_equalTo, available if HC_SHORTHAND is defined.

See also:
HCIsEqual
#define hasDescription (   match  )     HC_hasDescription(match)

hasDescription(match) - Evaluates whether [item description] satisfies a given matcher.

Examples:

  • hasDescription(startsWith(@"foo"))
  • hasDescription(@"bar")

Synonym for HC_hasDescription, available if HC_SHORTHAND is defined.

match A matcher, or a value for equalTo matching.
